title: Dakine Quest Photo Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Quest Photo Pack, shown in Black.
Pack features:
- Padded sleeve fits most 15" laptops
- Dual access padded camera block
- Deployable rain cover
- Separate top compartment
- Pre-curved weight distributing waist belt
- Tripod carry system
- Vertical board carry straps
- Water bottle pocket
- Customizable padded camera partitions
